---
title: Tandoori Lamb Chop with Golden Lentils
description: Chef Andre is the mastermind behind tonight’s delicious yoghurt-marinated lamb recipe. When asked about the inspiration behind this recipe, here’s what he said: “Using yoghurt as a marinade makes the tandoori spice mix spice warm rather than super spicy. Also, when you grill meat that's been marinated in yoghurt you get a lovely charred flavour which works really well with lamb!” We’re sold, and we’re sure you will be too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tandoori-lamb-chop-wk41-7ff1cfa4.jpg
